executives to make the case

00:09:01.600 --> 00:09:05.410
for the importance of this archive
and the need to have it included

00:09:05.410 --> 00:09:07.350
in the library's collections.

00:09:07.350 --> 00:09:10.530
I want to thank Tess Delprete,

00:09:10.530 --> 00:09:13.230
who is here representing
the State Department also,

00:09:13.230 --> 00:09:18.420
