due to weather issues, and he
trained also Afghan journalists

00:09:58.830 --> 00:10:03.280
for AMRC 1986 and then return
to Kabul for this project

00:10:03.280 --> 00:10:05.600
for the Library of Congress.

00:10:05.600 --> 00:10:09.870
Steve has come all the way from
California to be with us today

00:10:09.870 --> 00:10:13.360
and make, as we pointed out,
all the way from Boston.

00:10:13.360 --> 00:10:16.330
I want to thank Library
Services, here represented

00:10:16.330 --> 00:10:20.020
by the Associate Librarian
for Library Services,

00:10:20.020 --> 00:10:22.560
Mark Sweeney [assumed spelling],
and the Director of Collection

00:10:22.560 --> 00:10:24.140
and Services, Selina Zinkam
[assumed spelling], who,

