unfortunately, could not be with us.

00:10:26.630 --> 00:10:30.840
But they supported -- they have
provided support for this project

00:10:30.840 --> 00:10:34.770
and have recognized its importance.

00:10:34.770 --> 00:10:38.260
My thanks go to my colleague,
Greg Lukow, who is sitting here,

