00:11:42.890 --> 00:11:47.560
My role in this project has been
that of bringing people together,

00:11:47.560 --> 00:11:50.330
who needed to work together.

00:11:50.330 --> 00:11:54.540
I met Haji Daud eight years ago
when he came to the library to see

00:11:54.540 --> 00:11:57.650
