collection in Kabul.

00:12:01.270 --> 00:12:04.740
Endangered because it was
threatened by war, by conflict,

00:12:04.740 --> 00:12:08.230
but also by natural elements,
such as dampness, extreme cold,

00:12:08.230 --> 00:12:11.610
or extreme heat, insects, etcetera.

00:12:11.610 --> 00:12:14.250
Together we worked to get
copyright permissions,

00:12:14.250 --> 00:12:16.060
set up an operational budget,

00:12:16.060 --> 00:12:18.600
and get the library's
approval for the project.

00:12:18.600 --> 00:12:22.210
Within Ambassador Peter Tomsen,
Jim Hoagland [assumed spelling],

00:12:22.210 --> 00:12:24.060
