00:12:28.620 --> 00:12:29.920
Deanna Markham [assumed spelling],

00:12:29.920 --> 00:12:32.800
and explained the importance
of that archive.

00:12:32.800 --> 00:12:35.870
She gave me the green light to
pursue this project and agreed

00:12:35.870 --> 00:12:39.030
that the library should hold a
digital copy of these materials

00:12:39.030 --> 00:12:42.260
if we were able to
make this project work.

00:12:42.260 --> 00:12:45.590
For four years we searched
for funding for the project,

00:12:45.590 --> 00:12:51.110
and then in a perfect Library
of Congress way, perfect story,

00:12:51.110 --> 00:12:53.460
someone from the Department
of State came

