battlefield of the Cold War,

00:22:50.120 --> 00:22:52.320
one that had spread the collapse

00:22:52.320 --> 00:22:56.570
of the last political totalitarian
empire of the 20th century.

00:22:56.570 --> 00:22:59.110
But then, sadly and immediately,

00:22:59.110 --> 00:23:01.840
Afghanistan became
a major battlefield

00:23:01.840 --> 00:23:05.250
against the first religious
totalitarian movement

00:23:05.250 --> 00:23:11.250
of the 21st century, and that
conflict tragically continues today

00:23:11.250 --> 00:23:13.050
without letup.

