with cultural programming,

00:47:28.180 --> 00:47:29.720
which I thought was so important.

00:47:29.720 --> 00:47:33.860
We got along very well
professionally and otherwise.

00:47:33.860 --> 00:47:38.810
And in this sea of war,
refugees, spies, and vast amounts

00:47:38.810 --> 00:47:42.960
of well-meaning money, of all
the Afghans that I had met,

00:47:42.960 --> 00:47:49.460
Haji Daud struck me as an extremely
honest and trustworthy man.

00:47:49.460 --> 00:47:53.960
So with Nick and my
recommendation, Boston hired --

00:47:53.960 --> 00:47:58.310
