00:47:58.310 --> 00:48:01.520
He is a politically
astute media professional

00:48:01.520 --> 00:48:07.230
who had wonderful contacts with
all the Afghan resistance parties,

00:48:07.230 --> 00:48:09.710
as well as with exiled
Afghan journalists.

00:48:09.710 --> 00:48:11.610
When I say all of the
resistance parties,

00:48:11.610 --> 00:48:16.680
