with [inaudible] groups

00:48:16.680 --> 00:48:18.980 position:56%
from different parts of Afghanistan.

00:48:18.980 --> 00:48:24.810
Haji Daud was talking [inaudible]
commanders, journalists and,

00:48:24.810 --> 00:48:29.610
as you've come to learn many of you
through the big [inaudible] divide,

00:48:29.610 --> 00:48:34.110
this was in Afghanistan
very important.

00:48:34.110 --> 00:48:38.150
We started our first
week training session,

00:48:38.150 --> 00:48:41.710
